adoh, jujur saja kalo ko su tra sayang (su tra sayang)

su kenyang ko kas makan-makan deng janji
ko bilang hati ni su dapa sasi
su trada lagi kapa bubar jang baku dapa lagi

kalau su tra sayang, jang ko buang-baung
adoh sungguh kasihan, tinggal bulan depan
su tunggu perkawinan ko tambah deng beban
baru nanti nikah kapan ?

nona mata garida
pakar di nomor lidah
ko keturunan ninja
hilang ju tiba-tiba
cara, parah, ko pancing sampe sa marah
dara, darah sifat setan yang ko bawah
ko mama, ko bapa dong pasti paling malu
deng ko tu pu sifat yang su paling terlalu
jadi mulai sekarang anggap su trada
dari pada harap ko ju bikin apa
sa su cape baku dapa
tinggal toki gila kapa

kalau su tra sayang, jang ko buang-baung
adoh sungguh kasihan, tinggal bulan depan
su tunggu perkawinan ko tambah deng beban
baru nanti nikah kapan ?

kalau su tra sayang, jang ko buang-baung
adoh sungguh kasihan, tinggal bulan depan
su tunggu perkawinan ko tambah deng beban

ko bikin sa ni cape, cape,,,,

snippet.title: Wheels On The Bus - Learn Colors with Colorful Buses - Kids Songs and Nursery Rhymes
snippet.description:
📢Listen on SPOTIFY - http://listento.loolookids.com/bestofloolookids😁
📢𝐃𝐨𝐰𝐧𝐥𝐨𝐚𝐝 𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐦𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐜 𝐚𝐩𝐩: http://onelink.to/looloo

Join the wheels on the bus for a simple color lesson with bright surprise eggs. The bus rolls in. An egg pops open. A bold red object appears. The next stop shows blue. Then you see yellow, green, orange, and purple. Each reveal keeps the rhythm of the song so children link a tune to every new shade.

The animation is clear and slow. Kids can point at the screen and say the color. The lyrics repeat key words to help memory. Toddlers clap, sing, and learn colors without fuss. Preschoolers match the egg colors to toys at home. The melody stays gentle so it never distracts from the color focus.

Parents can use the video during playtime or a quick study break. Teachers can add it to circle time for an easy visual aid. Anyone who enjoys kids songs, nursery rhymes, or colorful stories will find value here. It is a short, friendly way to blend wheels on the bus fun with the surprise eggs craze while children learn colors at their own pace.

*** 
LIRIK :  "BULE JEPANG"

Jegeg mula seken jegeg, yen di kampung iluh dadi bungan desa.. 
Kulitne putih ebok ne lantang, meklieb barak mirip cara bule jepang.. 

Yen mejalan bangkiang iluh e lantang, jegegne mengayang ngalahang kembang setaman.. 

Depang anake nyampahang beli, kone i lutung ane ngidamang bulan.. 
Bulan e galang duwur mesunar, nanging i lutung beten meguyang

Boya beli tusing sadar diri, nanging rasa sayang beli ane ngalahang.. 
Tusing misi gaya manipulasi, jani iluh payu ngenyakin beli.. 

         Oh.. Yen ada nak e iri, nyelek nyelekang beli sing kal lawan kel bales aji kenyeman.. 
         Depang iya ngomongan ye sing ngelah kemampuan, beriak air tanda tak dalam.. 

Reef:
 
Iraga metunangan, ulian pada ngelah perasaan..iluh nyak ken beli, murni ulian bermain hati.. 

_Alisne nyerarit me don intaran, kenyemne manis semanis madu.. 
_adi mula bajang incaran, di hatin beli adi nomer satu..
